}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== Brand model: "CSOUNDU C08-41"
This is an USB sound card with one microphone input and one headphones output, both 3.5mm audio jacks.
The card is detected in Linux as "C-Media Electronics, Inc. Audio Adapter (Planet UP-100, Genius G-Talk)"
